{"id":281640,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-西安、杭州文化活动遭警方取消/","date":"2013-03-01T18:15:26Z","modified":"2013-03-01T18:15:26Z","title":"维权网 | 西安、杭州文化活动遭警方取消","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）临近两会，西安、杭州文化活动遭警方取消。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span>著名作家冉云飞原计划携新书《给你爱的人以自由》到西安万邦书店做推广签售活动，具体安排分别为：第一场，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>点</span><span>，在南二环太白立交西段怡丰城</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3F</span><span>，万邦•今日阅读城市文化空间；第二场：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14:30</span><span>小寨十字东路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">126</span><span>号万邦图书城二楼木光书吧。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>晚，冉云飞在西安的读者签售会被警方取缔，寒夜里赶来的大批读者徒唤奈何。另外，西安当地书友原计划</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>晚在西安小寨十字东路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">126</span><span>号万邦图书城二楼木光书吧举行的迎新春诗会，也被书店方面以装修的名义取消原定活动，西安当地数名书友此前还因此活动遭警方约谈。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另据著名学者傅国涌的微博，他接到电话，原定</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日晚</span><span>他主持的《傅国涌忆许良英》讲座也被取消。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height